description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Beginner Elliptical Workout - PYRAMID LEVELS | 10 Minutes' from the channel Sunny Health & Fitness.
The workout falls under Cardio/Elliptical.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Ready to break a sweat and boost your fitness journey? Join Sunny Trainer, Dana, for an easy 10-minute Beginner Elliptical workout that's packed with effective, pyramid-style intervals. In just a short amount of time, you'll gradually increase and decrease your resistance levels, building strength and endurance for a stronger you!

Time Stamps:
00:20—Level 1 – Warm-up: Ease into the workout with a comfortable level of resistance to get your body ready.

01:20—Level 2: Start the pyramid with a slight increase in resistance.
01:50—Level 3: Gradually up the challenge to level 3.
02:20—Level 4: Feel the burn as you progress to level 4.
02:50—Level 5: Push yourself to level 5 for an added challenge.
03:20—Level 6: Maintain your momentum at level 6.
03:50—Level 7: Conquer level 7 with determination.
04:20—Level 8: Reach your peak resistance at level 8.
04:55—Level 7: Step down slightly to level 7.
05:23—Level 6: Gradually decrease to level 6.
05:53—Level 5: Lower the resistance to level 5.
